A visible name cannot be declared again.

[codeblock, $code("bst"):
    score = 10

    if score > 0:
        -- Invalid: score already exists.
        score Int = 20
    ;
]

Choose a different name instead:

[codeblock, $code("bst"):
    score = 10

    if score > 0:
        doubled_score = score * 2
    ;
]

Reassigning a mutable binding is different. That changes the existing binding
instead of creating another one.
